https://www.tutorialsteacher.com/articles/ref-keyword

To pass the value type variables by reference.

class Program
{
    static void Main(string[] args)
    {
        int myNum = 10;
        ProcessNumber(ref myNum); //must use ref to pass the parameter by reference 
           
        Console.WriteLine(myNum);
        Console.ReadLine();
    }
 
    public static void ProcessNumber(ref int num)
    {
        num = 100;
    }           
}

Output:
100
